description:
Luke tells of the Third Missionary Journey, including Pauls long stay in Ephesus where he had to deal with Scevas sons and Demetrius. Timothy and Philip tell the end of the Third Missionary Journey. The basis for this episode is Acts 18-20.

Scripture
Acts 18: 22-23, Acts 19: 1-41, Acts 20: 1-38

Director: Phil Smith
Stars: David Smith, Paul Christian, Troy Powell
